  Question: AI company reaches an all-time high.
  Desc: The company reported strong earnings and investors are excited.The stock
    has already gained 20% today.
  cmt1: This stock will double!
  cmt2: Don't miss the AI revolution!
  cmt3: Easy money!
  CorrectOption: 4
  CorrectWhatHappenDec: After researching, you discovered the rally was driven by
    strong earnings. Understanding the reason helped you make an informed decision
    instead of following the crowd.
  CorrectLesson: Always understand why an asset is moving before investing.
  WrongWhatHappenDec: You acted without checking why the stock was rising. Although
    the news was positive, buying without research could expose you to unnecessary
    risk.
  WrongLesson: Excitement should never replace research.
